{
  "texts": [
    "The whole CRISP-DM cycle is repetitive.",
    "It can be divided into two groups:",
    "(1) the development phase is the group of the first five steps; and (2) the deployment phase, which is critical for real production.",
    "In 2015, the IBM Analytics Solutions Unified Method for Data Mining/Predictive Analytics (ASUM-DM) (IBM 2015) has been considered an extended and refined CRISP-DM.",
    "It has five phases: (1) Analyze, (2) Design, (3) Configure and Build, (4) Deploy, and (5) Operate and Optimize."
  ]
}